## HTTP REST API

### GET /health

```bash
curl http://localhost:50101/health
```

**응답**: 200 OK

---

### GET /api/sessions

```bash
curl http://localhost:50101/api/sessions
```

**응답**:
```json
{
  "sessions": [
    {
      "sessionId": "session_1",
      "programName": "Test Program",
      "createdAt": "2026-02-20T10:00:00Z",
      "state": "PAUSED"
    }
  ]
}
```

---

### GET /api/session/:sessionId

```bash
curl http://localhost:50101/api/session/session_1
```

**응답**:
```json
{
  "sessionId": "session_1",
  "programName": "Test Program",
  "stack": [ /* ... */ ],
  "actors": [ /* ... */ ]
}
```

